d":"2a52795275c2f29458302ee9f6b5a7d2d7d4e350","tid":472060,"uid":804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T08:53:10.000Z","msg":"一係買棍LW<br />\n一係買DSG PIRELLI"},{"pid":"93f4c4e6bd646c14879abb76b3b22b5d53a628aa","tid":472060,"uid":137946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T13:45:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一係買棍LW<br />\n一係買DSG PIRELLI</blockquote><br />\nDsg pirelli 係咪馬力多啲？"},{"pid":"c7e3f4ad89bff1006eb431bae311c82f114f63c2","tid":472060,"uid":143849,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T19:40:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>一係買棍LW<br />\n一係買DSG PIRELLI</blockquote><br />\nDsg pirelli 係咪馬力多啲？</blockquote><br />\n手三十隻到 去到230匹<br />\n原裝5代200隻"},{"pid":"1d3a099b83e77e209796a8affc5b59142fe66a09","tid":472060,"uid":804,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T17:12:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>一係買棍LW<br />\n一係買DSG PIRELLI</blockquote><br />\nDsg pirelli 係咪馬力多啲？</blockquote><br />\n跟K04 turbo 等於一部GOLF R<br />\n只不過係頭碌車<br />\nGTI 跟K03 turbo"},{"pid":"8297051114d5ec44c05d852cea7c756ef7b84ebe","tid":472060,"uid":150826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-24T15:40:59.000Z","msg":"MK5應該襟揸過MK6,不過MK5鯡型就真係麻麻"},{"pid":"3ae2a9477772a557877f20647ed6230c71cde56b","tid":472060,"uid":105366,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-27T10:25:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>一係買棍LW<br />\n一係買DSG PIRELLI</blockquote><br />\nDsg pirelli 係咪馬力多啲？</blockquote><br />\n馬力唔係重點。<br />\n重點係DSG轉波超快，轉數唔跌而又冇自動波動力流失既問題。<br />\n我老婆部MK5得199匹但燈位起步或上highway永遠放到啲三百幾匹棍波或自動波既V8 Mustang或Camaro影都唔見。<br />\n<br />\nDSG有自動波既方便加棍波既動力傳送兩者大成。<br />\n有佢你架車唔使好高馬力都好夠玩。"},{"pid":"ee6de5dd81ac255507d77209ed7ed93fece7ccbc","tid":472060,"uid":12523,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-27T14:24:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>一係買棍LW<br />\n一係買DSG PIRELLI</blockquote><br />\nDsg pirelli 係咪馬力